remedy.entities

Class Request

  • java.lang.Object
    • remedy.entities.Request
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CustomRequest

    public class Request
extends java.lang.Object
implements CustomRequest
    This class response for create custom request of KBForm. The KBForm for this object must be only:

    1. FormName.KB_DECISION_TREE_TEMPLATE

    2. FormName.KB_HOW_TO_TEMPLATE

    3. FormName.KB_KNOWN_ERROR_TEMPLATE

    4. FormName.KB_REFERENCE_TEMPLATE

    5. FormName.KB_PROBLEM_SOLUTION_TEMPLATE

    These object fields is populated based on filedID from FieldIDs

        Parameters:
        entry - The clear entry of KB remedy article request.
        formName - The template form from FormName
        requestID - The requestID is related Article
        articleID - The articleID is related KBForm
        webUrl - The web url KB article
        categories - Remedy categorization of Article
        articleAttachments - The path/fileName pair of Remedy article attachments. Those attachments were downloaded to file system (MainTask.pathContentFiles) by use of Article.setArticleAttachments(Entry, String) from Remedy KB article.
        pathContentFiles - The path to media files where they will be downloaded.

      • setOriginalContent

        public void setOriginalContent(com.bmc.arsys.api.Entry entry,
                               java.lang.String formName)
        This method set request content to originalContent field.

        For specific formName run specific method:

        1. FormName.KB_REFERENCE_TEMPLATE - getRefTempContent(Entry)

        2. FormName.KB_HOW_TO_TEMPLATE - getHowToTempContent(Entry)

        3. FormName.KB_KNOWN_ERROR_TEMPLATE - getKnownErrorTempContent(Entry)

        4. FormName.KB_DECISION_TREE_TEMPLATE - getDecisionTreeTempContent(Entry)

        5. FormName.KB_PROBLEM_SOLUTION_TEMPLATE - getProblemSolutionTempContent(Entry)

        Specified by:

        Parameters:
        entry - The clear entry of KB remedy article request.
